      "patch": "@@ -0,0 +1,8 @@\n+created: 2025-12-19\n+title: Changelog Plugin v1.1.0\n+intro: >-\n+  This release improves documentation and guidance across the changelog plugin. Updates\n+  include better CLI usage examples with correct flag positioning, enhanced release\n+  title documentation, and clearer guidance on writing plain text titles for changelog\n+  entries. All improvements focus on helping users follow best practices when managing\n+  changelogs."
